Armor Proficiency					KEY:Style Shifter ~ Armor Proficiency												CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ShifterClassFeatures.StyleShifterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																																																																																																			DESC:A style shifter is proficient with light armor but not with shields.																																																																																																																																																																	ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|TYPE=ArmorProfLight																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.17
Natural Strikes						KEY:Style Shifter ~ Natural Strikes													CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ShifterClassFeatures.StyleShifterClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.Extraordinary																																																																																																																DESC:A style shifter is considered to have Improved Unarmed Strike for the purposes of feat prerequisites and can apply the effects of feats that have Improved Unarmed Strike as a prerequisite to her shifter claws. This alters shifter claws.																																																																																																																							SERVESAS:ABILITY=FEAT|Improved Unarmed Strike																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.17
Style Shifting						KEY:Style Shifter ~ Style Shifting													CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ShifterClassFeatures.StyleShifterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																						DEFINE:StyleShiftMins|0				DESC:A style shifter gains access to style aspects. A style aspect provides benefits only while the style shifter is in the style feat stance associated with the appropriate aspect (such as Boar Style with Form of the Boar). He can shift into his style aspect for %1 minutes per day. The duration need not be consecutive but must be spent in 1-minute increments. A style shifter can shift into a style aspect as a free action as part of entering a style feat's stance. Otherwise, shifting into a style aspect is a swift action, while ending the effect is a free action that can be taken only on the style shifter's turn. He can shift between any aspects he has during the duration without additional cost.|StyleShiftMins																																																																																																							BONUS:VAR|StyleShiftMins|3+ShifterLVL																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.17
Style Mastery						KEY:Style Shifter ~ Style Mastery													CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ShifterClassFeatures.StyleShifterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																															DESC:A style shifter gains a bonus style feat. He does not need to meet the prerequisites of the feat.	DESC:Instead of a style feat, the style shifter can choose to instead gain a wildcard style slot. Whenever he enters one or more styles, he can spend his wildcard style slots to gain feats in those styles' feat paths (such as Panther Claw if he enters Panther Style) as long as he meets their prerequisites. Each time he changes styles, he can also change these wildcard style slots.																																																																																																																																																																		BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Shifter Style Feat|1+floor(ShifterLVL/5)																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.17
Form of the Wild					KEY:Style Shifter ~ Form of the Wild												CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ShifterClassFeatures.StyleShifterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																							DEFINE:StyleShiftHours|0			DESC:A style shifter gains the ability to turn into other creatures. This functions as a druid's wild shape ability, except he does not gain the ability to turn into an elemental. The shifter's effective druid level is equal to his class level. He can use this ability %1 of hours per day. This duration does not need to be consecutive, but must be spent in 1-hour increments. For abilities that function based on uses of wild shape, each hour of form of the wild counts as a use.|StyleShiftHours																																																																																																																																																															BONUS:VAR|StyleShiftHours|ShifterLVL/3																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.17
