# Style aspects
Form of the Boar					KEY:Style Shifter ~ Form of the Boar												CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ShifterClassFeatures.StyleShifterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																DESC:Once per round when you hit a single foe with two or more unarmed strikes, you can tear flesh. When you do, you deal an additional 1 point of bleed damage with the attack.	DESC:When you tear flesh, the target becomes sickened for 1 round.|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,8	DESC:Whenever you confirm a critical hit, you can attempt an Intimidate check to demoralize a target within 30 feet as an immediate action.|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,15																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.17
Form of the Crane					KEY:Style Shifter ~ Form of the Crane												CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ShifterClassFeatures.StyleShifterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																DESC:You reduce the penalty on attack rolls for fighting defensively by 1, to a minimum penalty of 0. 	DESC:When an attack misses you, you can move 5 feet as an immediate action without provoking attacks of opportunity.|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,8	DESC:When an attack misses you, you can move up to half your speed as an immediate action without provoking attacks of opportunity.|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,15																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.17
Form of the Dragon					KEY:Style Shifter ~ Form of the Dragon												CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ShifterClassFeatures.StyleShifterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																DESC:You gain a +1 dodge bonus to your AC for each ally you charge through when charging, up to a total equal to your Dexterity modifier (minimum +0).	DESC:Your unarmed strike's damage die increases by one step against shaken targets.|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,8	DESC:whenever you confirm a critical hit against a shaken target, the target becomes frightened for 1 round.|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,15																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.17
Form of the Monkey					KEY:Style Shifter ~ Form of the Monkey												CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ShifterClassFeatures.StyleShifterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																DESC:You gain a +%1 bonus on damage rolls while prone.|max(0,WIS)	DESC:You can craw up to half your speed as a move action.|PREVARLT:ShifterLVL,15	DESC:Whenever a creature provokes an attack of opportunity from you, that creature is considered flat-footed against your attack.|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,8	DESC:Whenever you take a 5-foot step, you are treated as if you were still in your original space for the purposes of flanking others until the start of your next turn (though you can't use this aspect to provide flanking for yourself), and you can crawl up to your full speed as a move action.|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,15																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.17
Form of the Panther					KEY:Style Shifter ~ Form of the Panther												CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ShifterClassFeatures.StyleShifterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																							DEFINE:PantherFormBonus|0			DESC:You gain a +%1 bonus to damage rolls for retaliatory unarmed strikes made with Panther Style.|PantherFormBonus	DESC:If a creature misses an attack of opportunity against you prompted by your movement through a threatened square, you can make a retaliatory unarmed strike against that creature, even if you would not normally be able to make any more retaliatory strikes this turn.|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,15																																																																																																																																																																																					BONUS:VAR|PantherFormBonus|max(0,WIS)	BONUS:VAR|PantherFormBonus|max(0,WIS)|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,8																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.17
Form of the Snake					KEY:Style Shifter ~ Form of the Snake												CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ShifterClassFeatures.StyleShifterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																DESC:Once per round when you hit a single foe with two or more unarmed strikes and deal piercing damage on your turn, you knock that foe off-balance. The foe is flat-footed until the start of its turn.	DESC:A foe you knock off-balance can't take attacks of opportunity until the start of its turn and remains flat-footed until the end of its turn.|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,8	DESC:When you confirm a critical hit, the target is knocked off-balance and provokes attacks of opportunity from you and your allies.|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,15																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.17
Form of the Snapping Turtle			KEY:Style Shifter ~ Form of the Snapping Turtle										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ShifterClassFeatures.StyleShifterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																DESC:You double your shield bonus to AC from Snapping Turtle Style.	DESC:You still gain your shield bonus to AC from Snapping Turtle Style even when you don't have one hand free.|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,8	DESC:There is a 10%% chance that critical hits and sneak attacks fail to affect you. This stacks with the light fortification armor special ability and similar effects.|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,15																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.17
Form of the Tiger					KEY:Style Shifter ~ Form of the Tiger												CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ShifterClassFeatures.StyleShifterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																							DEFINE:TigerFormDamage|0			DESC:On a successful bull rush, overrun, or trip combat maneuver, you deal %1 slashing damage to the target of the maneuver.|TigerFormDamage	DESC:If you hit with two or more unarmed strikes and deal slashing damage on your turn, you also rend your target, dealing damage equal to your unarmed strike plus 1-1/2 your Strength bonus.|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,15																																																																																																																																																																																																		BONUS:VAR|TigerFormDamage|STR	BONUS:VAR|TigerFormDamage|STR|PREVARGTEQ:ShifterLVL,8																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.17

